[Episode 10]

23
00:02:20,090 --> 00:02:22,860
Su Li.

24
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:28,120
Su Li.

25
00:02:41,060 --> 00:02:42,060
Su Li,

26
00:02:42,060 --> 00:02:43,060
you're awake.

27
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:51,460
How's my baby?

28
00:02:53,290 --> 00:02:54,220
Su Li,

29
00:02:54,220 --> 00:02:55,620
do you want to eat something?

30
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:57,560
I cooked some porridge.

31
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:59,760
How about having some to warm up first?

32
00:03:05,060 --> 00:03:06,560
What's with the baby?

33
00:03:09,890 --> 00:03:10,620
The doctor said the priority

34
00:03:11,090 --> 00:03:13,090
for you is to help your body recover,

35
00:03:13,660 --> 00:03:15,060
not anything else.

36
00:03:23,290 --> 00:03:23,890
My baby...

37
00:03:24,620 --> 00:03:25,920
Is it okay?

38
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:33,460
It's okay, right?

39
00:03:59,100 --> 00:04:06,200
[Episode 10]
[Monster Kill]

40
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:26,620
Shuheng,

41
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:27,890
have some milk.

42
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,490
I'm sorry about the other day.

43
00:04:41,460 --> 00:04:43,160
I shouldn't have lost my temper with you.

44
00:04:44,060 --> 00:04:45,220
I've forgotten about it.

45
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:50,920
I knew you wouldn't stay mad at me.

46
00:04:53,460 --> 00:04:54,560
Has Su Li...

47
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,490
been in touch with you?

48
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:57,160
No.

49
00:04:58,820 --> 00:04:59,220
Why did you ask?

50
00:05:00,860 --> 00:05:01,560
Just wondering.

51
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:09,960
Stop reading.

52
00:05:11,460 --> 00:05:12,660
Let's go shopping tomorrow.

53
00:05:14,090 --> 00:05:15,090
I have a shooting gig tomorrow.

54
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:16,320
Why don't you

55
00:05:16,620 --> 00:05:17,420
take my card?

56
00:05:24,090 --> 00:05:24,690
Tomorrow,

57
00:05:24,690 --> 00:05:26,290
I'll get the advance payment
for my next play.

58
00:05:26,620 --> 00:05:27,420
Take it.

59
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:30,260
I'm not sure.

60
00:05:31,220 --> 00:05:32,060
Treat it as my way

61
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:33,160
of making it up
for not being able to be with you.

62
00:05:36,220 --> 00:05:37,420
I know you're the best to me.

63
00:06:34,820 --> 00:06:36,620
I decided to keep the child.

64
00:06:36,620 --> 00:06:38,090
Since I've decided to keep it,

65
00:06:38,090 --> 00:06:39,490
I must give it the best.

66
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:46,760
I reserve it.

67
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:47,820
This one and this

68
00:06:48,490 --> 00:06:49,490
and that red one

69
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:51,220
and this one.

70
00:07:42,260 --> 00:07:43,490
Okay, it's settled then.

71
00:07:43,660 --> 00:07:44,420
Pleasure doing business with you.

72
00:07:44,420 --> 00:07:44,720
Okay.

73
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:45,820
I'll head out.

74
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:47,090
Goodbye, Mr. Zhao.

75
00:07:55,460 --> 00:07:56,290
Any more issues?

76
00:07:58,960 --> 00:08:00,060
Why leave at the sight of me?

77
00:08:02,420 --> 00:08:03,220
No such thing.

78
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,060
Just realized there's some work left

79
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:05,920
that I have to do.

80
00:08:06,460 --> 00:08:07,490
Two minutes of your time.

81
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,060
I have a favor to ask.

82
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:14,060
No need to be so formal.

83
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:15,920
What is it?

84
00:08:17,490 --> 00:08:18,360
I need you to help me

85
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:20,490
bring down Zhang Shuheng.

86
00:08:26,520 --> 00:08:27,420
You know it.

87
00:08:27,890 --> 00:08:29,260
I've been with Shuheng for years.

88
00:08:29,690 --> 00:08:31,120
I couldn't bring myself

89
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:32,390
to ruin him.

90
00:08:35,490 --> 00:08:36,460
What about me?

91
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:39,120
You knew me long

92
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,760
before you knew Zhang Shuheng.

93
00:08:43,620 --> 00:08:44,960
How could you stand by

94
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,090
and watch him ruin me?

95
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:50,320
Su Li,

96
00:08:51,060 --> 00:08:53,260
let me give you some advice
as your old friend.

97
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:54,960
There's no need

98
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:57,060
for a marriage to end in total disaster.

99
00:08:57,520 --> 00:08:58,920
It won't do you any good.

100
00:09:04,290 --> 00:09:06,160
You've been enjoying my jokes for so long.

101
00:09:07,490 --> 00:09:09,320
Time for you to pay up.

102
00:09:13,460 --> 00:09:15,360
I really didn't mean to keep it
from you.

103
00:09:15,860 --> 00:09:16,690
Do you have any idea

104
00:09:16,690 --> 00:09:17,890
how I fought with Zhang Shuheng

105
00:09:17,890 --> 00:09:19,860
defending your honor?

106
00:09:20,460 --> 00:09:22,020
Besides, he promised me
over and over again

107
00:09:22,020 --> 00:09:23,260
that he'll confess to you.

108
00:09:23,260 --> 00:09:24,720
So I didn't say anything to you at all.

109
00:09:25,620 --> 00:09:27,060
Even if I wronged you,

110
00:09:28,620 --> 00:09:29,660
I still can't do

111
00:09:30,220 --> 00:09:30,920
what you asked me to.

112
00:09:38,620 --> 00:09:40,260
How do you have these photos?

113
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:41,290
There're more.

114
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:48,460
The rookies you found.

115
00:09:48,460 --> 00:09:49,720
You introduced them
to other companies first,

116
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:51,490
before your company,

117
00:09:52,090 --> 00:09:53,090
taking two kickbacks.

118
00:09:54,220 --> 00:09:55,690
Plus, these rookies have to give you 20%

119
00:09:55,690 --> 00:09:58,220
of their earnings in private.

120
00:09:58,220 --> 00:09:59,690
You're quite something.

121
00:10:02,660 --> 00:10:03,620
Su Li,

122
00:10:03,620 --> 00:10:04,960
let's talk it over.

123
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:06,320
If I send the photos

124
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:07,760
to your company,

125
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:09,090
there would be no way you can survive

126
00:10:09,090 --> 00:10:10,920
in this industry.

127
00:10:10,920 --> 00:10:12,420
Can you help me now?

128
00:10:22,060 --> 00:10:22,560
Su Li,

129
00:10:23,890 --> 00:10:25,160
I'm really sorry.

130
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:28,060
I initially thought Zhang Shuheng

131
00:10:28,060 --> 00:10:29,620
just wanted to have some fun.

132
00:10:29,620 --> 00:10:30,360
So an apology is all it takes

133
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:31,760
for me to forgive you, huh?

134
00:10:34,460 --> 00:10:35,890
Show me some real actions!

135
00:10:52,460 --> 00:10:53,420
I have to take this.

136
00:10:56,260 --> 00:10:56,820
Hello?

137
00:10:56,820 --> 00:10:57,860
Shuheng,

138
00:10:57,860 --> 00:10:59,090
why is there no money on the card?

139
00:10:59,620 --> 00:11:00,060
No money?

140
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:03,020
But a payment should come through today.

141
00:11:03,660 --> 00:11:04,360
You have no idea

142
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:06,820
how humiliating I was
when the card was declined

143
00:11:06,820 --> 00:11:07,760
in the store.

144
00:11:09,420 --> 00:11:10,090
Okay.

145
00:11:10,090 --> 00:11:10,890
I'll take a look.

146
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:24,120
(The number you have dialed
can't be reached at the moment.)

147
00:11:32,820 --> 00:11:33,220
Okay.

148
00:11:33,220 --> 00:11:33,620
Ready to roll.

149
00:11:35,420 --> 00:11:36,420
Director, your phone.

150
00:11:40,220 --> 00:11:40,660
Hello?

151
00:11:47,180 --> 00:11:47,540
Okay.

152
00:11:49,660 --> 00:11:50,360
Come on, everyone.

153
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:51,520
Let's call it a day.

154
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:52,020
Wrap it up.

155
00:11:52,420 --> 00:11:54,660
Thanks, Director.

156
00:11:55,620 --> 00:11:57,490
Let's wrap it up.

157
00:12:01,690 --> 00:12:02,060
Director,

158
00:12:02,490 --> 00:12:04,120
why suddenly stop shooting?

159
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:04,860
Your company called

160
00:12:04,860 --> 00:12:07,160
and canceled the shooting.

161
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:08,360
Move fast, everyone.

162
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,660
Take down that light.

163
00:12:18,660 --> 00:12:19,180
Mr. Li,

164
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:21,980
why was my shooting canceled?

165
00:12:22,620 --> 00:12:23,880
Also, the money that was supposed
to be deposited today

166
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:24,880
hasn't arrived yet.

167
00:12:25,350 --> 00:12:26,780
It's not only today's shooting,

168
00:12:27,880 --> 00:12:29,280
all your future jobs

169
00:12:29,980 --> 00:12:30,950
have been canceled.

170
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,020
Why?

171
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:39,680
The company has known it was you

172
00:12:40,400 --> 00:12:42,560
who leaked the news

173
00:12:42,560 --> 00:12:43,360
about Lu's

174
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:44,400
sky-high remuneration.

175
00:12:44,400 --> 00:12:45,900
Do you know how much it cost us

176
00:12:45,900 --> 00:12:47,460
because of what you did?

177
00:12:47,930 --> 00:12:49,600
Lu is still criticized to this day.

178
00:12:50,130 --> 00:12:51,530
There's no chance to make a comeback.

179
00:12:53,300 --> 00:12:54,560
We've decided
to terminate contract with you

180
00:12:55,660 --> 00:12:56,760
and press charges asking

181
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:57,800
for compensation.

182
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:01,560
Haven't I made enough money
for the company over the years?

183
00:13:02,730 --> 00:13:04,130
You're ditching me

184
00:13:04,930 --> 00:13:06,160
over such a nobody?

185
00:13:06,800 --> 00:13:07,330
Don't forget

186
00:13:07,330 --> 00:13:09,100
I'm the mainstay in the company.

187
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:11,860
Yes.

188
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:13,560
Over the years,

189
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:16,000
you've made some money for us,

190
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:18,060
but the resources all came from Su Li.

191
00:13:19,130 --> 00:13:20,260
Now, you divorced.

192
00:13:20,930 --> 00:13:21,800
Do you think you can handle

193
00:13:21,800 --> 00:13:22,330
on your own?

194
00:13:23,130 --> 00:13:25,260
Maybe we have to spend extra money
and resources

195
00:13:25,260 --> 00:13:26,330
to maintain your influence.

196
00:13:27,460 --> 00:13:29,100
And the cheating scandal

197
00:13:29,100 --> 00:13:30,330
between you

198
00:13:30,330 --> 00:13:32,400
and Chen Yingying is like a ticking bomb.

199
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:33,960
It may go off at any second.

200
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:35,760
A star with lapsed morals like you,

201
00:13:35,760 --> 00:13:36,500
who sabotages the company,

202
00:13:36,500 --> 00:13:38,760
retaliates coworkers
and has a indiscreet private life,

203
00:13:38,760 --> 00:13:40,200
which company would dare to hire?

204
00:13:42,760 --> 00:13:44,460
Zhao Wen,

205
00:13:44,460 --> 00:13:45,700
say something.

206
00:13:45,700 --> 00:13:46,860
You've been my agent for years.

207
00:13:46,860 --> 00:13:48,330
Don't you know me?

208
00:13:48,330 --> 00:13:50,530
I'm nothing but loyal to the company.

209
00:13:55,330 --> 00:13:56,330
Loyal?

210
00:13:59,560 --> 00:14:01,160
That's the funniest thing I've ever heard.

211
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:03,060
Just a few days ago,

212
00:14:03,060 --> 00:14:04,900
I saw you meeting with another company.

213
00:14:06,130 --> 00:14:06,800
Don't tell me

214
00:14:06,800 --> 00:14:08,730
you were just having some tea with them.

215
00:14:15,400 --> 00:14:16,460
Fine.

216
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:19,460
You all set me up.

217
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:23,060
You make it hard for me

218
00:14:23,800 --> 00:14:26,130
and I'll make you all suffer.

219
00:14:41,130 --> 00:14:42,000
Where are you going?

220
00:14:44,530 --> 00:14:45,930
Why are you in my car?

221
00:14:45,930 --> 00:14:47,930
Did you report me

222
00:14:47,930 --> 00:14:49,530
about leaking Lu's remuneration?

223
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:54,900
Shuheng, hear me out.

224
00:14:55,460 --> 00:14:57,930
I never meant for it to happen.

225
00:14:57,930 --> 00:15:00,160
And I didn't know it was you
at the beginning.

226
00:15:00,160 --> 00:15:01,530
If...

227
00:15:01,530 --> 00:15:02,360
What if?

228
00:15:05,300 --> 00:15:06,760
If Su Li didn't threaten me

229
00:15:06,760 --> 00:15:07,400
and asked me to report you,

230
00:15:07,400 --> 00:15:08,930
I would never do so.

231
00:15:09,700 --> 00:15:11,100
Su Li?

232
00:15:11,100 --> 00:15:12,500
I'm telling the truth.

233
00:15:17,300 --> 00:15:18,160
Su Li...

234
00:15:18,930 --> 00:15:20,800
wants to doom me to death.

235
00:15:24,130 --> 00:15:25,400
It hurts.

236
00:15:26,260 --> 00:15:27,530
I'm come after you later.

237
00:16:43,060 --> 00:16:45,740
[Writing Magic of Love Stories
Speaker: Su Li]

238
00:16:47,100 --> 00:16:47,600
Ms. Su Li,

239
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:48,960
twenty minutes left.

240
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:52,500
I want to add a video

241
00:16:52,500 --> 00:16:54,500
before the first scene...

242
00:16:54,500 --> 00:16:55,060
Su Li.

243
00:16:57,730 --> 00:16:58,800
We have something private to talk about.

244
00:17:02,060 --> 00:17:02,960
You agreed

245
00:17:03,660 --> 00:17:04,560
to divorce amicably.

246
00:17:06,060 --> 00:17:07,530
Why you still come after me?

247
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,700
You even promised not to betray me.

248
00:17:13,460 --> 00:17:14,460
How's that turning out?

249
00:17:17,060 --> 00:17:17,460
Yes.

250
00:17:18,700 --> 00:17:19,660
I cheated on you.

251
00:17:20,260 --> 00:17:22,660
But what's the point
of scheming against me

252
00:17:22,660 --> 00:17:23,660
endlessly?

253
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:28,260
I thought

254
00:17:28,760 --> 00:17:30,260
getting in a relationship is

255
00:17:30,260 --> 00:17:31,800
for mutual support.

256
00:17:34,130 --> 00:17:35,130
Who'd know

257
00:17:35,130 --> 00:17:37,100
you're the one who betrayed me.

258
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:40,130
What does it take for you to stop?

259
00:17:47,930 --> 00:17:49,160
I want you to die,

260
00:17:50,760 --> 00:17:52,400
to go to hell.

261
00:17:52,930 --> 00:17:53,760
Su Li,

262
00:17:54,860 --> 00:17:55,800
don't cross the line.

263
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:57,460
If you push me too hard,

264
00:17:57,930 --> 00:17:59,800
who knows what I might do?

265
00:18:00,460 --> 00:18:01,260
Go!

266
00:18:01,260 --> 00:18:02,400
Go to explain everything to Mr. Li!

267
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:03,900
Tell him you're behind all of this!

268
00:18:05,530 --> 00:18:08,130
What's wrong with pushing you?

269
00:18:08,130 --> 00:18:09,700
You're a spineless

270
00:18:09,700 --> 00:18:10,860
coward

271
00:18:10,860 --> 00:18:12,260
who's been living off me

272
00:18:12,260 --> 00:18:13,860
and relying on me to give you work.

273
00:18:13,860 --> 00:18:14,330
Without me,

274
00:18:14,330 --> 00:18:16,260
you're nothing.

275
00:18:16,260 --> 00:18:19,000
Even dogs know to wag their tails
at their owners,

276
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:20,730
you only know to bark at me.

277
00:18:25,130 --> 00:18:26,200
Shut up.

278
00:19:39,360 --> 00:19:40,530
Call the police.

279
00:19:41,730 --> 00:19:42,530
Call the police.

280
00:20:15,900 --> 00:20:17,530
According to People's Republic of China's

281
00:20:17,530 --> 00:20:19,100
Public Security Administration
Punishment Law,

282
00:20:19,100 --> 00:20:21,260
I'm here to mediate the dispute
between you.

283
00:20:22,360 --> 00:20:23,330
Ms. Su,

284
00:20:23,330 --> 00:20:24,260
do you have any demands?

285
00:20:25,060 --> 00:20:25,460
Yes.

286
00:20:27,100 --> 00:20:28,300
I demand

287
00:20:28,300 --> 00:20:29,500
severe punishment for the criminal.

288
00:20:29,500 --> 00:20:31,860
Throw Zhang Shuheng in jail
for reflection.

289
00:20:32,700 --> 00:20:34,130
Officer,

290
00:20:34,130 --> 00:20:36,460
